item.title: CVE-2023-21404|2023-05-08T00:00:00 -- n%2Fa -- axis%20os
item.description: AXIS OS 11.0.X - 11.3.x use a static RSA key in legacy LUA-components to protect Axis-specific source code. The static RSA key is not used in any other secure communication nor can it be used to compromise the device or any customer data.
